{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":18399,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"史料是怎么保证其非片面性的呢…","timestamp":1592841823,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18401,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"是的，所谓抽象和具体，也就是理论要结合实例。螺旋式提高自己的历史观，政治观。","timestamp":1592841836,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18419,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 凡是历史都是阶级性的，凡是人所记载就无绝对公正一说，或许是某阶级眼里的公正","timestamp":1592841908,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18451,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 多看吧，不断修正自己的逻辑，慢慢就能分辨史料里自洽的部分了","timestamp":1592842070,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18462,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"问题是人们常常会先树立一个史观，然后去找尽可能多的史料来解释自己的观点","timestamp":1592842100,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18514,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 害，先自己树立正确的，再影响别人吧，不怕辩论，谁逻辑硬就能影响谁","timestamp":1592842368,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":18762,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3150,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 史料必然是片面性的，应当反思为什么会有“客观性”这种虚妄的标准","timestamp":1592843435,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3150,"reply":7,"tag":null,"text":"#3134 我觉得认识历史要从史料到史观再到史料，也就是马克思说的“具体—抽象—具体”。关键是树立最普适的史观，也就是找到最能解释尽可能多史料的逻辑","timestamp":1592841740,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782583,"url":"","vote":{}}}